dc_title_s: Law Enforcement Response Districts Waupaca County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents law enforcement response districts in Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2020. [The data set represents the jurisdictional boundaries for the various units of local government within Waupaca County, Wisconsin. The data is represented using polygons stored in a Geodatabase. The data is updated annually. The current publication date is January, 1 2008.]
